kpi_info.title: RRC SETUP FAIL DUE TO AC UL POWER
kpi_info.use: The number of RRC setup failures caused by Admission Control because of uplink power limitation. M1001C3 is also updated along with this counter. UPDATED: When the RNC decides to reject the RRC connection request because of uplink power admission control.
